tasks.implementationGuide:
Supabase MCP의 execute_sql 또는 SQL Editor에서 다음 실행:
1. CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS cases_user_id_created_at_idx ON cases(user_id, created_at DESC);
2. CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS ai_usage_logs_user_id_created_at_idx ON ai_usage_logs(user_id, created_at DESC);
3. 인덱스 생성 확인: SELECT indexname, tablename FROM pg_indexes WHERE tablename IN ('cases', 'ai_usage_logs');
